title: Veggie Club
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Buffet, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Argentinian, Latin American
description: Small takeaway offering a pay-by-weight buffet. You'll find an array of grilled vegetables, pasta dishes, salads plus quiche/tortilla bar, and a tiny fruit bar. Note that some of the tortilla options contain egg. Location near Facultad de Medicina underground station - please send exact map coordinates to happycow!
